# Universal AI Business Automation Platform — Architecture & Implementation Plan

## Overview

**FlowBot** is a config-driven, multi-tenant AI automation backend. The same codebase serves any business — a restaurant, a clinic, a tutoring centre — by swapping a YAML config and knowledge files. No code changes required.

---

